[컴포넌트 상세]

1. Auth Pages:
   - Login Form
   - Register Form
   - Forgot Password Form

2. Home:
   - Dispenser Status
   - Representative Dog Info

3. Dispenser:
   - Battery Level
   - Connection Status
   - Dispense Button

4. Dogs Info:
   - Dog Info Form
   - Dogs List

5. Auto Schedule:
   - Schedule Form
   - Current Settings
   - Next Dispense Time

6. My Page:
   - User Info
   - Delete Account
   - Terms of Service

[데이터 흐름]

User Input -> Event Handlers -> 
Page Rendering -> DOM Updates

[주요 함수]

- renderAuthPage()
- renderPage()
- handleLogin()
- handleRegister()
- handleForgot()
- initHome()
- initDispenser()
- initDogsList()
- initSchedule()
- initMyPage()
- showModal()
- closeModal()

